Yes...

01:22:31.161 --> 01:22:33.490
it was like going home...

01:22:34.780 --> 01:22:37.661
entering into a long since faded time.

01:22:38.597 --> 01:22:42.139
I knew I didn't have to search for her
any longer.

01:22:42.591 --> 01:22:44.738
She would find me.

